<div id="how-to-order">
  <h1>How to Order</h1>

  <h2>Ordering Options for Sonnax Product Lines</h2>

  <ol>
    <li>
      <h3>Transmission Specialties<sup>&reg;</sup> products</h3>
      <p>Contact a <strong>Sonnax Transmission Specialties<sup>&reg;</sup> Distributor</strong>. Authorized customers can place orders using the Speed Order form and selecting <strong>Transmission Specialties<sup>&reg;</sup></strong> from the drop-down menu.</p>

      <div class="locate-a-distributor">
        <p>Locate a Transmission Specialties<sup>&reg;</sup> Distributor</p>
        <select name="locate">
          <option value="0">USA</option>
        </select>

        <p class="submit"><input type="submit" value="Go"></p>
      </div>
    </li>

    <li>
      <h3>Torque Converter and High Performance Torque Converter products</h3>
      <p>Authorized customers can place an order using the online Torque Converter Catalog or <%= link_to 'Speed Order Form', speed_order_path %>. New converter parts buyers: Contact Sonnax for account requirements.</p>
    </li>

    <li>
      <h3>High Performance Transmission products</h3>
      <p>New High Performance Transmission parts buyers can contact a <%= link_to 'High Performance Transmission Distributor', high_performance_distributors_path %> or contact Sonnax for account requirements.</p>
    </li>

    <li>
      <h3>Allison<sup>&reg;</sup> Transmission Replacement products</h3>
      <p>Authorized customers can place an order using the Speed Order form and selecting Allison from the drop-down menu. New Allison parts buyers: Contact Sonnax for account requirements.</p>
    </li>

    <li>
      <h3>Harley Davidson<sup>&reg;</sup> Replacement products</h3>
      <p><%= link_to 'Contact a distributor of Sonnax Harley Davidson<sup>&reg;</sup> Replacement Products.', harley_distributors_path %></p>
    </li>

    <li>
      <h3>Ring Gear Products</h3>
      <p><%= mail_to 'webrg@sonnax.com', 'E-Mail us', :class => 'email' %> for quotes and other information.</p>
    </li>

    <li>
      <h3>Power Train Savers<sup>&reg;</sup> and Driveline Products</h3>
      <p><%= mail_to 'info@sonnax.com', 'E-Mail us', :class => 'email' %> for quotes and other information.</p>
    </li>
  </ol>

  <p><%= link_to 'Payment and shipping options for international customers.', international_shipping_and_payment_path %></p>

  <h2>Other Options</h2>
  <p>If the information above did not answer your questions, feel free to contact Sonnax directly via the following information:</p>
  <p><strong>Call us:</strong> (800) 843-2600 or (802) 463-9722, Monday through Friday, 8:30 am - 5:00 pm ET</p>
  <p><strong>E-Mail us:</strong> <%= mail_to 'info@sonnax.com', 'info@sonnax.com', :class => 'email' %> or <%= mail_to 'internationalsalesteam@sonnax.com', 'internationalsalesteam@sonnax.com', :class => 'email' %> for international customers</p>
</div>